         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... says: «If ...»</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... having said (= given) his permission ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... they obtain ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... if it is ... years ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... is ... life. || In this manner ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... we have been born ...</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
         <div type="comments">
